{{Bio}}
'''Makhosi Busisiwe Khoza'''i [[Afrika-Dzonga|Mu-Afrika Dzonga]] wa n'watipolitiki na loyi a a ri Xirho xa Palamende xa vandla ra ANC loyi a nga tirha tani hi mutshama-xitulu wa Portfolio ya Vutirhela-Mfumo na swa Tihofisi (Public Service and Administration). Khoza u tirhe eka Portfolio Committee ya Economic Development (Nhluvuko wa swa Ikhonomi). U tiveke ngopfu hi ku byela mupresidente Jacob Zuma leswo a suka eka xiyimo.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mg.co.za/article/2017-07-20-00-makhosi-khoza-i-am-willing-to-face-discipline|title=ANC MP Makhosi Khoza: I'm not going to apologise. If they kill me, so be it|first=Dineo|last=Bendile|publisher=Mail & Guardian|date=20 July 2017|accessdate=2 September 2017}}</ref>

== Dyondzo na khariya (ntirho) ==
U na digri ya PhD eka Public Administration na digri ya master's eka Social Science (Policy and Developmental Studies) yo huma eUniversity of Witwatersrand.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pa.org.za/person/makhosi-busisiwe-khoza/|title=Dr Makhosi Busisiwe Khoza|publisher=People's Assembly|accessdate=13 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tyi.co.za/news/local/dr-makhosi-khoza-an-unofficial-political-legend/|title=Dr. Makhosi Khoza. An unofficial political legend|last=Roodt|first=Tyler|date=2017-07-18|work=The Young Independents|access-date=2018-10-26}}</ref> I fellow eka nhlangano wa Aspen Global Leadership Institute.<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.pa.org.za/person/makhosi-busisiwe-khoza/#experience|title=Makhosi Busisiwe Khoza|website=People's Assembly|access-date=2018-10-26}}</ref>

Hi ku va na xipiriyoni eka mfumo na tikhampani, Khoza u tirhe eka Portfolio Committee ya Economic Development tani hi xirho xa  Palamende ku sukela  hi ti  4 Septembere 2017 ku fikela hi ti 21 Septembere ta lembe relero. Na swona a a ri xirho xa African National Congress (ANC), National Assembly, na xirho xa  AdHoc Committee xa ku langutana na ku langiwa ka Musirheleri wa Vanhu ku nga Public Protector.<ref name=":1" /> Hi ti 21 ta Septembere 2017, Khoza u tivisile ku rhizayina ka yena eka  ANC leswo a ta joyina matshalatshala yo lwa na mikhuva yo bola eka swa timali ta mfumo eAfrika Dzonga.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mg.co.za/article/2017-09-21-breaking-makhosi-khoza-leaves-anc-to-join-anti-corruption-organisation|title=Makhosi Khoza leaves ANC to work with anti-corruption organisation|date=21 September 2017|publisher=Mail & Guardian}}</ref>

Hi ti 1 ta Disemba 2017, Khoza u tivisile leswo u ta sungula vandla lerintshwa ra tipolitiki, vito ra rona ku nga African Democratic Change<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/makhosi-khoza-launches-new-party-vows-not-to-make-same-mistakes-as-anc-20171201|title=Makhosi Khoza launches new party, vows not to make same mistakes as ANC|date=2017-12-01|work=News24|access-date=2019-06-25|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619113402/https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/makhosi-khoza-launches-new-party-vows-not-to-make-same-mistakes-as-anc-20171201|dead-url=yes}}</ref> leri a ri ta vumbiwa hi mintlawa ya  16 mintlwa leyitsongoya tipolitiki.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/politics/2017-11-27-makhosi-khoza-returns-to-politics-to-help-form-new-party/|title=Makhosi Khoza returns to politics to help form new party|access-date=2017-11-28|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://citizen.co.za/news/south-africa/1742938/makhosi-khozas-message-to-those-opposed-to-her-new-party/|title=Makhosi Khoza's message to those opposed to her new party|work=The Citizen|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref> Khoza u ve a rhizayina eka vandla ra African Democratic Change hi ti 22 Epreli 2018.<ref>{{cite web|title=Makhosi Khoza resigns from politics|url=https://www.heraldlive.co.za/news/2018-04-22-makhosi-khoza-resigns-from-politics/|date=2018-04-22|work=The Herald}}</ref>

== Ubantu alfabete ya ririmi ra XiZulu ==
Khoza i musunguri wa ririmi ra alfabete hi ku landza sisteme ya nandzeleriso leyi yi pfunaka ku dyondza ririmi ra  XiZulu. Khoza u tsarile buku ya textbook leyi yi tirhaka ku va xiseketelo xo tiya xa vutiviti eka swa lingwistiki hi ku tivisa mimpfumawulo yintshwa leyi landzelelanaku ku nga , Ubantu isiZulu Alphabetical Logic Order (UZALO). Buku ya yena ya textbook yi tirha tani hi makombandlela na thulusi ra tindzimi timbirhi leyi yi nga tirhisiwaka tani hi ndlela yo twisisa tindzimi ta Bantu to hambana-hambana.<ref name="Khoza2017">{{cite book|last=Khoza|first=Makhosi |title=Uzalo: IsiZulu Grammar Textbook|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4q8NugEACAAJ|year=2017|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-108-43061-6}}</ref>

